    "TimeDiff": "- \n1.35 hrs",
    "Notes": "<p data-start=\"184\" data-end=\"515\"><strong data-start=\"184\" data-end=\"196\">Summary:</strong><br data-start=\"196\" data-end=\"199\" />Received a call from <strong data-start=\"220\" data-end=\"231\">Heather</strong> at <strong data-start=\"235\" data-end=\"242\">KES</strong> regarding an issue with a <strong data-start=\"269\" data-end=\"285\">missing file</strong>. She had accidentally <strong data-start=\"308\" data-end=\"332\">overwritten the file</strong> and was seeking to recover the previous version. After attempting to recover the file through <strong data-start=\"427\" data-end=\"435\">M365</strong> and <strong data-start=\"440\" data-end=\"450\">iCloud</strong>, and checking on <strong data-start=\"468\" data-end=\"476\">iMac</strong>, the older version could not be found.</p><p data-start=\"517\" data-end=\"537\"><strong data-start=\"517\" data-end=\"535\">Actions Taken:</strong></p><ol data-start=\"538\" data-end=\"1184\"><li data-section-id=\"t9nob9\" data-start=\"538\" data-end=\"669\"><p data-start=\"541\" data-end=\"669\">Connected to <strong data-start=\"554\" data-end=\"571\">Heather&rsquo;s Mac</strong> and searched for the file, but was unable to locate the oldest version due to system limitations.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"1fmjryd\" data-start=\"670\" data-end=\"760\"><p data-start=\"673\" data-end=\"760\">Attempted recovery using <strong data-start=\"698\" data-end=\"706\">M365</strong> and <strong data-start=\"711\" data-end=\"721\">iCloud</strong> version history, but was unsuccessful.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"1351w0i\" data-start=\"761\" data-end=\"849\"><p data-start=\"764\" data-end=\"849\">Discovered that Heather has <strong data-start=\"792\" data-end=\"811\">two Mac devices</strong>, and one of them was <strong data-start=\"833\" data-end=\"848\">powered off</strong>.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"qovwc\" data-start=\"850\" data-end=\"906\"><p data-start=\"853\" data-end=\"906\">Stopped all <strong data-start=\"865\" data-end=\"889\">internet connections</strong> on both devices.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"1ooyhkg\" data-start=\"907\" data-end=\"985\"><p data-start=\"910\" data-end=\"985\">Powered on the <strong data-start=\"925\" data-end=\"943\">old Mac device</strong> that had the <strong data-start=\"957\" data-end=\"984\">old version of the file</strong>.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"q325pn\" data-start=\"986\" data-end=\"1057\"><p data-start=\"989\" data-end=\"1057\">Recovered the file with a <strong data-start=\"1015\" data-end=\"1040\">new naming convention</strong> and made a copy.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"f5te4n\" data-start=\"1058\" data-end=\"1136\"><p data-start=\"1061\" data-end=\"1136\">Re-enabled the internet connection and allowed <strong data-start=\"1108\" data-end=\"1123\">iCloud sync</strong> to complete.</p></li><li data-section-id=\"1u5nctp\" data-start=\"1137\" data-end=\"1184\"><p data-start=\"1140\" data-end=\"1184\">Successfully recovered the old file version.</p></li></ol><p data-start=\"1186\" data-end=\"1203\"><strong data-start=\"1186\" data-end=\"1201\">Next Steps:</strong></p><ul data-start=\"1204\" data-end=\"1268\"><li data-section-id=\"ia4k2\" data-start=\"1204\" data-end=\"1268\"><p data-start=\"1206\" data-end=\"1268\">No further steps required as the file recovery was successful.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"1270\" data-end=\"1340\"><strong data-start=\"1270\" data-end=\"1281\">Status:</strong> Issue resolved and file recovery completed; ticket closed.</p>",
